 As Magnus Prime shot at Hell beast. From under the
ground. Long metal spikes shot up through the dirt
right where rampages stomach would be. Righ through up
to 5 feet of the ground. When the spikes stopped 10
spikes jutted out side ways of each. From the top of
them formed proto's body. "Its good to be back." Hi
spark had been reconfigured by Magnus by the oracel
out of pitty due to thier shared experience in the
cell Galvatron kept them in.
